Chris,<br><br>
Your ideas may be original for you and I appreciate your thoughtfulness. I guess I get a little concerned when those ideas sound exactly like others.<br><br>
Only difference, though, is you do not attack those of us that served as so many others have.<br><br>
Someone several centuries ago said the soldiers are the first people to be called upon when things go bad. And the first to be forgotten when all is well again. So wha thas happen to us is not new nor is it unique to this country.<br><br>
If you really want to make a difference, vote in very election and not re-elect the same folks in office just because they are already there. Only then can we, together make a difference.<br><br>
Stay cool and thanks.
